  "text": "12-14 Brunner, Zhou, and Moon all reported union rates of 100%. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] Rancan et al reported non-union in only 1 patient of 29. [CITATION_4] In the current study, full bone union was obtained in all the patients. The mean time to union was consistent with literature at 15.7 weeks despite the patients being in the geriatric age group.",
